Bhajan name: Ab Maine Rasna Ka Fal Paaya
Ab Sonp Diya Is Jeevan Ka
Are Man Samajh - Samajh Pag Dhariye
Bin Laathi Ke Nikla Andha, Ram Se Koi Milade, Mujhe Ram Se Koi
Bhaj Man Mere Ram Naam Tu
Beet Gaye Din Bhajan Bina Re
Chaliye Chaliye Chaliye Shree Ram Sharan Chaliye
Dukhiyno Ke Sankat Jo Door Kare
Guru Agya Mein Nish Din Rahiye
Guru Charnan mein Sheesh Jhuka Le
Guru Darshan Bin Hamein na Jeena
Hath Vich Maala Nu Farr Ke, Dhyan Satguru Da
Hariye Na Himmat Bisariye Na Ram
Hari Ka Rang Mein Prabhu Ka Rang Mein
Hum Se Bhali Jungle Ki Chidiya
He Dukh Bhanjan Raghunath Haro Dukh Mere
Japo Ji Nitya Ram Ram Shree Ram
Jara Aa Sharan Mere Ram Ki
Jise Dekhta Hnu Vahi Roop Tera
Jagat Mein Ram Naam Hai Saar
Kaiyna Janma De Baad Chola Paaya
Kisi Bhaav Se Kisi Naam Se
Kaahe Ram Se Lo Na Lagai
Kanha Re Tu Radha Ban Ja
Koi Kahiyo re Prabhu Aavan Ki
Lali Mere Lal Ki - Ram Rang Laga
Lele Dard Paraya Karde Door Gum Ka Saya
Mere Rom Rom Shree Ram Pukaare
Man Chanchal Chal Ram Sharan Mein
Mujhpe Itni Kripa Bus Vidhata Rahe, Ram Ka Naam Hothon Pe Aata Rahe
Mere to Bas Ek Hi Ram
Meri Banh Pakad Lo Ek Baar
Mere Man Mandir Mein Ram Virajein
Mere Ram Raghunath Teri Jai Hove
Main to Unn Santno Ka Dass
Mann Lago Mero Yaar Fakiri Mein
Mere Dil Ka Swami Prabhu Ek Tu Hai
Patte Patte Daali Daali Mera Ram Vasda
Preeti Prabhu Se Jod Re Man
Prabhu Ji Tum Chandan Hum Paani
Paya Paya Maine Ram Ratan Dhan Paya
Ram Ab Aisa Var Main Paaun
Ram Mujhe Madhur Milan Mile Tera
Ram Main to Jab se Sharan Teri Aaya
Ram Do Nij Charno mein Sthan
Ram Naam Lo Lagi Ab Mohe
Ram Ab Sneh Sudha Barsa De
Ram Ras Barsyo Ri Aaj Mhare Aangan Mein
Ram Banu Tan Ko Taap na Jaai
Re Mann Hari Sumiran Din Ram
Suneri Maine Nirbal Ke Bal Ram
Satguru Mile Mere Saare Dukh Bisre
Torr De Saare Jag Ke Bandhan
Tum Taji Aur Kaun Paii Jaayun
Tera Jeevan Hai Nissaar Ram Ke Bhajan Bina
Tum Hi Main Hnu Main Hi Tum Ho
Tumko Jaana hai Jahan Tak Tu Hi Tu Hai
